https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harmonic_series_(music)

further extensions
-----------------------------------
Implement memory cell and parameterised freq\amp\phase
    or parameterised envelope
additional generators
    noise, constant
additional modifiers/combinators
    envelope, gating, limiter, hystersis, phase shift
saveable solutions (e.g. reuse saw-tooth)
random gen'd puzzles, import\exportable seed
some kind of highscore metrics. Number of components used

